Package ru.alvisid.pacs.repository.loader

Class EnumLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.alvisid.pacs.repository.loader.EnumLoader
  • @Component
public class EnumLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods to synchronize the enum classes with dictionaries classes which represents dictionary tables from data base. We don't need keep enums like entity and can save enums by ordinal values. Dictionaries classes have to be heir of the AbstractDictionary and be annotated with @MappedEnum which contains enum Class to mark the dictionary class that is represented by the enum.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Glushkov Evgeniy

        Parameters:

      • updateEnumValues

        private void updateEnumValues​(java.lang.Class<? extends java.lang.Enum> enumClass)
        Updates array field $VALUES of the constants in the specified enum class so that array index of the enum constant equals appropriate id from the dictionary table. Updates array field enumConstants in the Class of the enumClass because it is initialized before array field $VALUES, and has n-1 element.
        Parameters:
        enumClass - the enum class to apdate array field $VALUES.
